The video below is copyright free and can be used at will, without asking for authorization Watch the video Ahead of the FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022™, FIFA (www.FIFA.com) President Gianni Infantino has delivered a video message raising a “Green Card for the Planet” to highlight awareness on the protection of the environment. The initiative is linked to World Environment Day – celebrated annually on 5 June – the United Nations’ principal vehicle for encouraging awareness and action for this crucial subject. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of FIFA. Contact for African media: 
